OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fclear spells. Cloudier across eastern
OL,7,Fparts of Scotland and northeast
OL,8,FEngland. A patchy frost possible in
OL,9,Fthe countryside with mist and fog in
OL,10,Fprone spots. Remaining breezy across
OL,11,Fsouthwest England, especially along
OL,12,Fthe coasts and hills.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FMorning low cloud lifting to
OL,15,Fleave a fine day, with plenty of
OL,16,Fsunshine. Still breezy in the
OL,17,Fsouthwest. Warm for most, but
OL,18,Fremaining chilly along eastern coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
